        "subtitle-1": "Poured, Not Planned",
        "subtitle-2": "<p>Catching up with a friend in the heart of winter holds a special kind of magic. We’re referring to the kind of catch-up that doesn’t need a special occasion, a dress code, or a perfectly planned menu. Just a warm dish, a good bottle of red wine, and the comfort of people who feel like home.</p><p><strong>“At Alvi’s Drift, we believe the best moments in life are the simplest.”</strong></p><p>Winter doesn’t have to be about grand gestures. Sometimes it’s about saying, “Come over,” without warning. “I’m lighting a fire” or “I made stew”. The reds in our Signature Range and 221 Range will feel as easy and generous as the moment itself.</p><p>From couch catchups to spontaneous braais, these reds offer warmth, flavour, and an open invitation to make yourself at home. They are made for real life – full of character, smooth in texture, and easy to love.</p>",
